smbclient Cheat Sheet
Terence Priestley - pur3sneak

To launch use: smbclient
To display public shares on the server use: -L server
To connect to a share use: //server/share/
Connect with a specific username use: //server/share/ --user username
Connect with a specific workgroup use: //server/share --workgroup domain --user username
Connect with a specific username and password: //server/share --user username%password
Download a file from the server use: //server/share --directory path --command "get filename"
Upload a file to the server use: //server/share --directory path --command "put filename"
List the shares from a server anonymously use: --list=server --no-pass